Introduction

Ahn Hyo-jin, better known by her stage name LE, is a South Korean rapper, singer, songwriter, and record producer and the main rapper of the girl group EXID.

She was previously a member of the underground hip hop group, Jiggy Fellaz, performing under the stage name "Elly".

Sometime in 2022 she changed her stage name to her previous stage name, "Elly"
